The evidence with the title 'Revisiting Newt Gingrich's 1997 ethics investigation : NPR ' says Dec 8, 2011  ... This week, House minority leader Nancy Pelosi suggested she might release details of the 1990s ethics investigation into then-speaker Newt Gingrich. An investigative committee, on which Pelosi served, concluded that Gingrich had used tax-exempt funds for partisan purposes. 
